The package boost-accumulators is compatible with built-in CMake targets of FindBoost.cmake:

    find_package(Boost REQUIRED COMPONENTS accumulators)
    target_link_libraries(main PRIVATE Boost::accumulators)

or the generated cmake configs via:

    find_package(boost_accumulators REQUIRED CONFIG)
    target_link_libraries(main PRIVATE Boost::accumulators)
